REVENUE_MEASURE_KEY AND DRVD.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MONTH_NUM_INT = INV.DV_FISCAL_YEAR_MTH_NUMBER_INT AND DRVD.LAST_RECORD_FLG='Y' INNER JOIN $$SLSORDVWDB.N_SALES_ORDER_LINE SOL ON SOL. AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT 1 FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE MT2 WHERE MT2.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD = INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD AND MT2.XAAS_OFFER_ATRBTN_REV_LINE_KEY > 0 AND MT2.XAAS_OFFER_ATRBTN_REV_LINE_KEY = INV.XAAS_OFFER_ATRBTN_REV_LINE_KEY )
AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT 1 FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE MT4 WHERE MT4.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD = INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD AND MT4.ADJSMT_RBT_TRX_LIN_GL_DIST_KEY > 0 AND MT4.ADJSMT_RBT_TRX_LIN_GL_DIST_KEY = INV.ADJSMT_RBT_TRX_LIN_GL_DIST_KEY )
AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT 1 FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE MT5 WHERE MT5.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD = INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD AND MT5.DIRECT_CORP_ADJUSTMENT_KEY > 0 AND MT5.DIRECT_CORP_ADJUSTMENT_KEY = INV.DIRECT_CORP_ADJUSTMENT_KEY )
AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT 1 FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE MT6 WHERE MT6.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD = INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD AND MT6.ACCRUED_REV_TRX_KEY > 0 AND MT6.ACCRUED_REV_TRX_KEY = INV.ACCRUED_REV_TRX_KEY )
AND NOT EXISTS( SELECT 1 FROM $$FINLGLVWDB.MT_INV_REV_MEASURE MT7 WHERE MT7.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD = INV.REV_MEASURE_TRANS_TYPE_CD AND MT7.MERAKI_REV_TRX_KEY > 0 AND MT7.MERAKI_REV_TRX_KEY = INV.MERAKI_REV_TRX_KEY )
